{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.920", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.680", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.720", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wechselmodell als Regelfall\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.560", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das lehnt die SPD-Fraktion ab. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.760", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine gesetzliche Regelung f\u00fcr den Umgang des Kindes mit den Eltern findet sich bereits in \u00a7\u00a01684\u00a0BGB;\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.880", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Juristen sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.120", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein Blick ins Gesetz erleichtert die Rechtsfindung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.880", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort steht in Absatz\u00a01:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.520", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Kind hat das Recht auf Umgang mit jedem Elternteil\u00a0..."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.400", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In Absatz\u00a03 steht dann\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.760", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist entscheidend\u00a0\u2013:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.200", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Familiengericht kann \u00fcber den Umfang des Umgangsrechts entscheiden und seine Aus\u00fcbung\u00a0... "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.240", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4her regeln."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.040", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Davon haben die Gerichte bisher mehr oder weniger Gebrauch gemacht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.280", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Einige waren so mutig und haben das schon angeordnet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.960", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "teilweise auch im Wege der einstweiligen Anordnung unmittelbar nach der Trennung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.720", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Andere waren sich unsicher und haben das abgelehnt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.960", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der BGH hat nunmehr klargestellt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.000", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das durchaus m\u00f6glich ist und dass alle Modelle von \u00a7\u00a01684\u00a0BGB umfasst sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.280", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Kindeswohlprinzip ist ebenfalls im Gesetz geregelt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.760", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass alle Entscheidungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.920", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die zu treffen sind, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.400", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "immer das Kindeswohl im Blick haben m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.120", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Eine gesetzliche Regelung in Ihrem Sinne braucht es nicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.240", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im \u00dcbrigen wundert mich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.000", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine freiheitlich-demokratische Partei hier ein ganz bestimmtes Modell vorgeben und den Menschen die Entscheidungsfreiheit nehmen m\u00f6chte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zutreffend ist auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.760", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sich Eltern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.720", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ihr gemeinsames Sorgerecht zum Wohle des Kindes aus\u00fcben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.640", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auf ein Wechselmodell ohne gerichtliche Kl\u00e4rung einigen k\u00f6nnen und dies auch bereits getan haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.800", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese F\u00e4lle kommen erst gar nicht vor Gericht; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "101.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sehen wir gar nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "101.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.000", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin Dilcher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "107.920", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erlauben Sie eine Zwischenfrage der Kollegin Helling-Plahr?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "107.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.480", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Kollegin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.200", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es entsteht unweigerlich der Eindruck, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sowohl Sie als auch die Kollegen unseren Antrag nicht gelesen oder nicht verstanden haben oder ihn auch nicht verstehen wollten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.640", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht uns nicht darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.960", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir jeder Familie ein Wechselmodell aufdr\u00fccken wollen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.240", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben klargestellt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.960", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass in jedem Einzelfall Pr\u00fcfungen des Kindeswohls stattfinden m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.880", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir wollen das Wechselmodell zum Regelfall machen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.400", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht mehr und nicht weniger\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "143.720", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von dessen Basis aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "143.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.120", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie derzeit auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.960", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der konkrete Fall beurteilt werden muss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vor diesem Hintergrund bitte ich Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.280", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu Ihrer bisherigen Aussage noch einmal Stellung zu nehmen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.560", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.120", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich denke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.400", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben Ihre Frage gerade selbst beantwortet in dem Augenblick, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.040", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wo Sie gesagt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.680", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollten das als Regelfall. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.720", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genau das wollen wir nicht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.400", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In der Mehrzahl der F\u00e4lle ist es so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "176.600", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die \u00fcberwiegende Betreuung durch einen Elternteil und der Umgang des anderen Elternteils an Wochenenden und einzelnen Wochentagen leider immer noch die Regel ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "176.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.120", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil die gesellschaftlichen Rahmenbedingungen es heute gar nicht anders zulassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.160", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo gibt es denn M\u00f6glichkeiten einer zuverl\u00e4ssigen Betreuung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.080", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn beide Elternteile Vollzeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "190.800", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das eventuell noch im Schichtbetrieb, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "190.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.120", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "arbeiten wollen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.240", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo ist der finanzielle Ausgleich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.360", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn beide Elternteile vor\u00fcbergehend in Teilzeit arbeiten wollen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.400", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Voraussetzungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.720", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diese Rahmenbedingungen m\u00fcssen wir schaffen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.320", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daran werden wir arbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.320", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um ein Wechselmodell aufbauen zu k\u00f6nnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.800", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das nicht nur f\u00fcr mehr Eltern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.120", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern insbesondere f\u00fcr mehr Kinder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "210.880", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil wir das Kindeswohl im Blick haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "210.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.120", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch die Forderung der Linken nach \u00c4nderung des Unterhaltsrechts bzw. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.920", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dessen Anpassung ist f\u00fcr mich noch ein bisschen zu kurz gedacht; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.600", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da m\u00fcssen wir noch eine ganze Menge mehr erarbeiten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.400", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer bezahlt dann noch den Kindergarten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.920", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Schulb\u00fccher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.640", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Schulausfl\u00fcge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.560", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Geschenke f\u00fcr Freunde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.080", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bekleidung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.880", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vereinsbeitr\u00e4ge, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.360", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Taschengeld? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.800", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind strittige Fragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.840", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sicherlich noch weiter diskutiert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.160", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn sich Eltern streiten wollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.600", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann finden sie auch etwas, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.880", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wor\u00fcber sie sich streiten k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.560", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Am wichtigsten f\u00fcr die Kinder sind die Bindung des Kindes zu beiden Elternteilen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.840", 
   "id": "s000089", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deren Kommunikation und die gemeinsame Sorge. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.160", 
   "id": "s000090", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen wir also den Eltern und den Gerichten Spielraum, "
   ]
